        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A mute, gesticulating routine that is <em>meaningless madness</em> (@Check[type:performance|dc:20] to realize) and actively harmful to watch: each living creature within 60 feet observing it, @Check[type:will|dc:24] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1} (cumulative to 3); a success grants immunity to that ghost's pantomime for 24 hours. <strong>The harm is invisible</strong> — only @Check[type:perception|dc:24] notices minds dimming (roll the players' saves secretly until they know).</p>"
